Package: dbc
Title: Install and Use ADBC Drivers via dbc
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Bryce", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "bryce@example.com")
Description: Provides a single entry point for using any ADBC database driver
    from R. Drivers are installed on-demand via the dbc registry and exposed
    as standard DBI driver objects.
License: Apache License (>= 2)
